import React from 'react';
import { Container,Row,Col } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Index = () => (

  <Row>

    <Col xs={6}>2 of 3 (wider)</Col>
    <Col>3 of 3</Col>
  </Row>
  <Row>
    <Col>1 of 3</Col>
    <Col xs={5}>2 of 3 (wider)</Col>
    <Col>3 of 3</Col>
  </Row>
</Container>
  )
  export default Index
